Nuxwdogclient version 0.01
=========================

This module provides a Perl interface into the nuxwdog client C library.
As such, it requires the nuxwdog rpm (which contains the C/C++ nuxwdog
server and client libraries) to be installed in order to execute correctly.

The module comprises a Perl Extension module and a C shared library to 
make the relevant C calls into libnuxwdog.so. The module is compiled using
ExtUtils::MakeMaker.
  
INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

libnuxwdog.so.0

